OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,FThe UK's largest train operator's
OL,7,Fservices have been taken into public
OL,8,Fownership.
OL,10,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,11,Fheralded the nationalisation of Govia
OL,12,FThameslink Railway (GTR) as "a
OL,13,Fdefining moment in our reform of the
OL,14,Frailway".
OL,16,FGTR services carry more passengers
OL,17,Fthan any other operator in the UK,
OL,18,Faccounting for one in six train
OL,19,Fjourneys in Britain.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
