PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,FIts four brands - Southern,
OL,7,FThameslink, Great Northern and Gatwick
OL,8,FExpress - cover large swathes of south-
OL,9,Feast England and beyond.
OL,11,FThe Department for Transport (DfT) has
OL,12,Fcommitted to doubling the frequency of
OL,13,FGatwick Express services between
OL,14,FLondon Victoria and Gatwick Airport
OL,15,Ffrom December, and introducing more
OL,16,Fearly morning services on Saturdays
OL,17,Fand Mondays from this summer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,FIt also pledged to crackdown on
OL,7,Fgraffiti in Thameslink train toilets,
OL,8,Fupgrade signalling between Farringdon
OL,9,Fand Blackfriars to cut delays, and
OL,10,Fdeploy 110 new travel safe officers to
OL,11,Ftackle anti-social behaviour across
OL,12,Fthe network.
OL,14,FMs Alexander said: "From this Sunday,
OL,15,Fmillions of passengers across the
OL,16,FSouth East and East of England will be
OL,17,Ftravelling on rail services back in
OL,18,Fpublic hands - run for the public
OL,19,Fgood, not private profit.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,F"Bringing Britain's largest train
OL,7,Foperator into public ownership is a
OL,8,Fdefining moment in our reform of the
OL,9,Frailway.
OL,11,F"It gives us an opportunity to tackle
OL,12,Fthe bread and butter issues people
OL,13,Fwant, like driving down cancellations
OL,14,Fand improving the frequency of
OL,15,Fservices to Gatwick Airport.
OL,17,F"As we set up Great British Railways
OL,18,F(GBR), we're putting passengers first,
OL,19,Ffixing what's broken, and delivering a
OL,20,Frailway people can rely on."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,FGBR will be a new public sector body
OL,7,Fbringing responsibility for tracks and
OL,8,Ftrains under a single organisation for
OL,9,Fthe first time since privatisation in
OL,10,Fthe mid-1990s.
OL,12,FLegislation to create GBR was included
OL,13,Fin the recent King's Speech.
OL,15,FThe first train displaying GBR
OL,16,Fbranding was a Southern train unveiled
OL,17,Fin Brighton earlier this month.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
