OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,FGTR chief operating officer John
OL,7,FWhitehurst said: "This is a railway
OL,8,Fthat carries millions of people to
OL,9,Fwork, to school, and to see friends
OL,10,Fand family every single day.
OL,12,F"From this Sunday every one of them
OL,13,Fwill be on a publicly owned service,
OL,14,Fwhich is a responsibility we take
OL,15,Fseriously and one we have been
OL,16,Fpreparing for.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,F"We have spent the past year building
OL,7,Fthe foundations, and bringing even
OL,8,Fdeeper integration into our operations
OL,9,Fwith Network Rail, with a single focus
OL,10,Fon what's right for our customers and
OL,11,Fcommunities.
OL,13,F"That work means customers are already
OL,14,Fgetting a railway that's been
OL,15,Ftransforming, and public ownership
OL,16,Fgives us the chance to go further to
OL,17,Fdeliver the railway that millions of
OL,18,Fpeople across the South East deserve."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
