OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,FIn the mid-2010s, Southern's
OL,7,Fpassengers often suffered poor
OL,8,Fpunctuality and reliability.
OL,10,FThis particularly made headlines when
OL,11,Fit emerged the 7.29am departure from
OL,12,FBrighton to London Victoria failed to
OL,13,Farrive on schedule at 8.35am during
OL,14,Fany of the 240 attempts in 2014.
OL,16,FThe operator blamed this on high
OL,17,Fdemand and congestion.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,FThere was also a long-running
OL,7,Findustrial dispute between Southern
OL,8,Fand its drivers and conductors over
OL,9,Fstaffing issues, including a row about
OL,10,Fwho would operate train doors.
OL,12,FOn Sunday, GTR became the fifth
OL,13,Foperator to enter public ownership
OL,14,Funder the Government, following c2c,
OL,15,FGreater Anglia, South Western Railway
OL,16,Fand West Midlands Trains.
OL,18,FLNER, Northern, Southeastern and
OL,19,FTransPennine Express were already
OL,20,Fnationalised when Labour came to power.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
