PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780233072
OL,3,CGovia Thameslink Railway, UK's biggest
OL,4,Ctrain operator, is nationalised
OL,6,FChiltern Railways' services will be
OL,7,Fnext to transfer on September 20,
OL,8,Ffollowed by Great Western Railways on
OL,9,FDecember 13.
OL,11,FThe full public ownership programme is
OL,12,Fexpected to be completed by the end of
OL,13,Fnext year.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
